Title: An Act Changing the Name of Pozorrubio National High School to Benigno V. Aldana National Memorial High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 807
An Act Changing the Name of Pozorrubio National High School to Benigno V. Aldana National Memorial High School
Section 1. The name of Pozorrubio National High School in the Municipality of Pozorrubio, Province of Pangasinan, is hereby changed to Benigno V. Aldana National Memorial High School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
